{"kind": "callout", "id": "216c39cd9b6c2446", "section_id": "https://code.claude.com/docs/en/scheduled-tasks.md#compare-scheduling-options", "position": 0, "callout_kind": "tip", "text": "Use cloud tasks for work that should run reliably without your machine. Use Desktop tasks when you need access to local files and tools. Use `/loop` for quick polling during a session."}
